{"tid":1965226,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「保就業Loop loop loop」大法 政府助半年full pay不是夢","createTime":"2020-04-09T10:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T10:45:48.000Z","uid":254435,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d815a0ecf414ee8cae7d2f3b45237c32f466f27a","tid":1965226,"uid":254435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T10:33:08.000Z","msg":"與其靠滙豐looplooploop，不如睇下「保就業Loop loop loop」大法<br />\n<br />\n快d click 入內文學大法啦<br />\n<br />\n//如果此100名員工，根本不用交稅，即$9,000（政府資助）-$1,800（MPF）x 100人 x 6個月，相當於432萬元，半年full pay買樓簡直就不是夢。而且公司出糧仲可以扣稅，到年尾隨時蝕錢連稅都不用交！//<br />\n<br />\n【START噏人話】「保就業Loop loop loop」大法 政府助半年full pay不是夢（黎兆沖）<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/loopx3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Floopx3&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVYD442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=19b2b30e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/loopx3</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而網民口中的「保就業Loop loop loop大法」應該如何實行？<br />\n<br />\n首先你要是一個老闆，即先要開設一間公司，這會有一筆一次性成本。網上有不少「0蚊創業」的公司，公司註冊費1,720元連同商業登記費250元，再收取約2,000至3,000元的秘書費、地址及文件等費用；成本只是約5,000元，如果是轉讓公司，更加是2,000多元有交易。<br />\n<br />\n其次就是要請人，請一個「員工」半年成本如下：<br />\n月薪18,000元，半年人工10.8萬元，僱主、員工各5%的MPF供款，半年10,800元；<br />\n薪俸稅扣除MPF供款，應繳稅收入10.26萬元，以累計稅率最高的17%計為17,442元。<br />\n此表示，薪俸稅連同前述MPF供款，半年總成本28,242元。<br />\n<br />\n每名「員工」半年資助54,000元，扣除上述的「成本」，公司可袋25,758元。<br />\n如果「員工」整年收入根本不到13.2萬元的個人免稅額，就連1.7萬元的稅都慳返，公司可袋43,200元。<br />\n對每名「員工」而言，MPF戶口因加入此公司，而增加10,800元。<br />\n<br />\n以每月計，換做算式：$9,000（政府資助）-$1,800（MPF）-$2,907（稅）=$4,293，每月回報4,293元，好過所謂的滙豐派息大法多多聲！<br />\n<br />\n如果你的公司有10個員工，半年就至少袋政府25萬元（25758元 x 10）；100個員工（或開10間公司）就是250萬元。<br />\n<br />\n如果此100名員工，根本不用交稅，即$9,000（政府資助）-$1,800（MPF）x 100人 x 6個月，相當於432萬元，半年full pay買樓簡直就不是夢。而且公司出糧仲可以扣稅，到年尾隨時蝕錢連稅都不用交！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/948509242205511/posts/1299569727099459/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F948509242205511%2Fposts%2F1299569727099459%2F&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVYD442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=cfdee948\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/948509242205511/posts/1299569727099459/</a>"},{"pid":"0d4295a92f71d749ec0dc49f3c739e75e7146d20","tid":1965226,"uid":254435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98199a809b1caf4be6f1a0ea1e0b68f91b2d8122","tid":1965226,"uid":254435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T11:09:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea085236c6cc850106eabf69ec68b11994ac199","tid":1965226,"uid":295248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:03:25.000Z","msg":"請自己屋企人得唔得先😎"},{"pid":"e33b5fc0eee03d9a4d6519041c44e2fb94b557ac","tid":1965226,"uid":791,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3ea085236c6cc850106eabf69ec68b11994ac199","tid":1965226,"uid":295248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:03:25.000Z","msg":"請自己屋企人得唔得先😎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:09:54.000Z","msg":"點解唔得<br />\n我有FD已經求我幫佢打工了"},{"pid":"b0802c1e43b971ae2bde4297609825227329f801","tid":1965226,"uid":8000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:17:30.000Z","msg":"個問題係可唔可以即刻開公司先"},{"pid":"efee013f6208e4f4174b8f0896baa543c44c23de","tid":1965226,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0802c1e43b971ae2bde4297609825227329f801","tid":1965226,"uid":8000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:17:30.000Z","msg":"個問題係可唔可以即刻開公司先"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:22:24.000Z","msg":"開公司可以好快<br />\n但係開埋mpf就唔知趕唔得切<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowha